<!-- ********************************************************************** -->
<section><title>Thread Pool</title>
<!-- ********************************************************************** -->

<section><title>ice.thread_pool.size</title>

<section><title>Synopsis</title>
<synopsis>
ice.thread_pool.size=<replaceable>num</replaceable>
</synopsis>
</section>

<section>
<title>Description</title>
<para>
The number of threads in the thread pool. Default is 10.
<replaceable>num</replaceable> must be equal to or larger than 1.
</para>
